title: Sunny 1 bed w/ BRAND NEW kitchen! Dishwasher, laundry on site, pets ok
posting_body: Located on the raised first floor (up a flight of stairs)
Lots of windows and natural light throughout!
Queen-sized bedroom
The kitchen was gutted and rehabbed w/ new stainless steel appliances, including dishwasher
Shared paid laundry on site
Street parking only, there is no parking available for rent
Please be aware there is no outdoor space or central a/c
**Photos are of a similar unit in the building.
The size and layout and kitchen are the same.
The bathroom cabinets are white
Water/trash included, tenant pays gas (heat) and electricity
Pets okay, 2 max.
There are some restrictions for dogs
$65 application fee
$350 one-time non-refundable move-in fee (flat fee, not per person)
$300 one-time non-refundable pet fee per dog.
There's no fee for cats
Minimum 650 credit score required
When inquiring, please include your name, direct contact info (email and cell) and which apartment you are interested in
MTD Property Management
773-997-2624 (text or messaging here preferred @Natalie)
